            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a splash of <strong>milk</strong> to a shallow bowl</p><p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to another plate with the <strong>grated cheese</strong>, lots of<strong> pepper </strong>and a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and mix it all together – these are your <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1597676535021-x200.jpg",
