    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the<strong> halloumi</strong> in to 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">[12]</span> strips</p><p>Tip: First slice the halloumi in half lengthways and then slice each half into 3 strips</p><p>Coat the <strong>halloumi strips </strong>in the <strong>spice mix</strong> (make sure to tap off any excess!)</p><p>Add the <strong>coated halloumi strips</strong> to the <strong>milk </strong>and finally press them into the <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs </strong>firmly to coat evenly – these are your <strong>breaded halloumi strips</strong></p>",
