    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a baking tray with <strong>tin foil</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>breaded halloumi strips</strong> to the tray and top them with any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 10-15 min or until golden – these are your<strong> crispy halloumi strips</strong></p>",
